John Lewis UK store sales up 15 . 6 % in week . The John Lewis Partnership said its UK weekly department store sales rose 15 . 6 percent in the week to June 14 from the same week a year earlier . In the 20 weeks to June 14 , sales were up 9 . 6 percent . Total sales , including the Waitrose supermarket group , rose 8 . 4 percent in the latest week and 7 . 0 percent in the 20 - week period . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 5109 
